### Polaris Altair ###
Ah, I see you've happened upon the operating manual of R&D's greatest creation. Feast your eyes upon P0L@R15, a robotic copy of yours truly.

R&D was enormously proud to show this to me.
I had them all fired, of course. It is easy on the eyes, though, if I do say so myself.

